HEADWORD: gambling
<hw>gambling</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[p. pr. of <er>gamble</er>.]</ety>
<def>the act of playing for stakes in the hope of winning (including the
payment of a price for a chance to win a prize); <as>as, his
<ex>gambling</ex> cost him a fortune</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> gaming, play.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

